# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Lær mer"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"Vi jobber hardt for å utvide denne brukerveiledningen og forbedre OpenShot "
"Video Editor, men hvis du står fast og ikke vet hvor du skal henvende deg, "
"har OpenShot flere kilder for ytterligere informasjon."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot har flere `YouTube-veiledninger <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ tilgjengelig for å hjelpe deg å "
"lære mer."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot har et `Reddit-brukersamfunn <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedikert til at brukere hjelper brukere, svarer på spørsmål og diskuterer "
"videoredigering og OpenShot-emner."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ønsker å bidra til å forbedre denne brukerveiledningen, `se "
"kildekoden på GitHub <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/"
"doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du har oppdaget en ny feil, vennligst `Rapporter en feil <https://www."
"openshot.org/issues/new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du trenger profesjonell støtte, kan du åpne en sak ved å sende en "
"melding til support@openshot.org eller `avtale en samtale <https://calendly."
"com/openshot-support/desktop>`_."
